│ I have failed to solve this issue multiple times. My previous attempts were unsuccessful because I could not locate the source of the miscompilation. I will try a new, more systematic  │
│ approach.                                                                                                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The miscompilation is in the `instcombine` pass. A `select` instruction with `nnan` and `nsz` flags is transformed, but these flags are not propagated to the new instruction.           │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The transformation is:                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ `select nnan nsz (fcmp olt %x, 0.0), %x, -0.0`                                                                                                                                           │
│ becomes                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ `select (fcmp oge %x, 0.0), -0.0, %x`                                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ This is a canonicalization that swaps the `select` arms and inverts the `fcmp` predicate. The bug is that the new `select` instruction is created without the `nnan` and `nsz` flags     │
│ from the original.                                                                                                                                                                       │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The transformation is happening because `instcombine` tries to canonicalize `select` instructions. It seems to prefer certain `fcmp` predicates (like `oge`) over others (`olt`),        │
│ leading it to invert the predicate and swap the `select` arms.                                                                                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ I will search for the code that performs this canonicalization. A key part of this transformation is inverting the comparison predicate. I will search for `getInversePredicate` in      │
│ `InstCombineCompares.cpp`, as this is where comparison instructions are canonicalized. An `fcmp` with a single `select` use is a prime candidate for such a transformation.              │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ grep -n -C 10 "FCmpInst &I" llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineCompares.cpp                                                                                                      │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                      │
