│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ This is a canonicalization. The most likely place for this is a generic `select` folder that swaps arms and inverts the condition. The code I found in                                   │
│ `llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineSelect.cpp` for `fmin`/`fmax` canonicalization is the only place that performs this exact transformation (`CreateSelect` with swapped arms   │
